網絡資料分析與模式：作業十二實作

助教 杜承軒 2021.06.11

利用本週提供的範例資料 csv files進行以下的動態網絡分析 


library(networkDynamic);library(tsna);library(ndtv);library(tergm);library(statnet)

setwd("D:/1092NT/Data/DyNet")
DE=read.csv('Sample_DynamicEdges.csv')
DN=read.csv('Sample_DynamicNodes.csv')
E=read.csv('Sample_Edgelist.csv')
N=read.csv('Sample_VertexAttributes.csv')
node=c("Third artist in lat. 10525","Hospitaller Master")
  1. 在Rmarkdown的html檔呈現動態網絡的animation。
net=network(E,N,c("vertex.id","name","region"),F,F)
DynNet=networkDynamic(net,edge.spells=DE,vertex.spells=DN,verbose=F)
## Edge activity in base.net was ignored
compute.animation(DynNet,slice.par=list(start=1255,end=1325,interval=1,aggregate.dur=20,rule="any"))
render.d3movie(DynNet,displaylabels=F,output.mode="htmlWidget",
               vertex.tooltip=function(slice)
                 sprintf("<b>Name:</b>%s<br><b>Region:</b>%s",slice%v%"name",slice%v%"region"))
  1. 節點名稱為”Third artist in lat. 10525”的Forward path 與transmission tree。
id=N$vertex.id[N$name==node[1]]
Path=tPath(DynNet,v=id)
plot(Path, cex.main=.8,edge.label.col="red",edge.label.cex=.6)

plotPaths(DynNet,Path,displaylabels=F,vertex.col="white",edge.label.col="transparent")

transmissionTimeline(Path,jitter=T)

  1. 比較上述節點與節點”Hospitaller Master”的時序degree變化趨勢。 （用line chart呈現與比較）
id2=N$vertex.id[N$name==node[2]]
DN$onset=1257
DN$terminus=1325
DynNet=networkDynamic(net,edge.spells=DE,vertex.spells=DN,verbose=F)
## Edge activity in base.net was ignored
DynDeg=tSnaStats(DynNet,"degree",start=1255,end=1324,time.interval=1,aggregate.dur=20)

plot(0,0,type='n',xlim=c(1255,1325),ylim=c(0,4),xlab="Time",ylab="Degree")
lines(1255:1324,DynDeg[,id],col='red',lwd=2)
lines(1255:1324,DynDeg[,id2],col='blue',lwd=2)
legend("topright",legend = node,col=c('red','blue'),lty=1)
